#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Don't pick up items."
msgstr "不要拾取物品。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "You can pick up items now."
msgstr "你现在可以拾取物品了。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Don't bash obstacles."
msgstr "不要破坏障碍物。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "You can bash obstacles."
msgstr "你可以破坏障碍物。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Stay awake."
msgstr "保持清醒。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Sleep when you feel tired."
msgstr "感到疲倦时再睡觉。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Stay quiet."
msgstr "保持安静。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Tell me when you need something."
msgstr "需要什么时告诉我。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Leave corpses alone."
msgstr "别碰尸体。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Smash zombie corpses."
msgstr "砸碎僵尸尸体。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Leave doors open."
msgstr "让门开着。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Close the doors."
msgstr "关上门。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Open doors to get where you're going."
msgstr "开门以便前往目的地。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Don't walk through closed doors."
msgstr "不要穿过关闭的门。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "If you hear a noise but can't see the source, move to investigate it."
msgstr "如果听到声响但看不到来源，就移动去调查。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Don't investigate noises that you can't see."
msgstr "不要调查你看不到的声响。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Set up pickup rules."
msgstr "设置拾取规则。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Clear all overrides."
msgstr "清除所有覆盖项。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Never mind."
msgstr "算了。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Here, use this serum."
msgstr "来，用这支血清。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Why should I do that?"
msgstr "我为什么要这么做？"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "It will help us survive."
msgstr "这能帮助我们生存下去。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "You won't stand a chance without it. You have to take it."
msgstr "没有它你毫无胜算。你必须接受它。"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "Huh? Wh-what's happening to...me......master?"
msgstr "嗯？发……发生什么了……我……主人？"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid "You're my maid now. Understood?"
msgstr "你现在是我的女仆了。明白吗？"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid ""
"It seems the serum made you more than just a woman...well, you're my maid "
"either way. (FUTANARI)"
msgstr "看来血清让你不仅仅是女人……好吧，不管怎样，你都是我的女仆。（扶她）"

#: .\npcs\TALK_MAID_ALLY.json
msgid ""
"Why can't I remember...I-I understand. Please take care of me...master."
msgstr "为什么我记不起来……我……我明白了。请照顾我……主人。"

